President Donald Trump congratulates Tun Dr. Mahathir Mohamad on being sworn in as the new Prime Minister of Malaysia. He also congratulates all Malaysians on their participation in a competitive and peaceful election campaign. The relationship between the United States and Malaysia is based on strong people-to-people ties, shared democratic values, and commercial relations. The United States is committed to working closely with Malaysia to strengthen their Comprehensive Partnership and tackle common international and regional challenges.